		<p style="font-family: 'Arial', 'Helvetica', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.25em; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0 6px 5px 6px;">Residents of Cambodia's capital city used to have little access to safe drinking water; now more than 90 percent of homes have it.</p>
		
